OL,3,CMan jailed for kicking, throttling and
OL,4,Cspitting on partner
OL,6,FA 51-year-old man from Jersey has been
OL,7,Fjailed for four years and three months
OL,8,Fafter he punched, kicked, slapped,
OL,9,Fthrottled and spat on his partner at
OL,10,Ftheir home.
OL,12,FThe Royal Court also sentenced John
OL,13,FSebastian Nicolle to a ten-year
OL,14,FDomestic Abuse Protection Order and an
OL,15,Findefinite notification order.
OL,17,FThe sustained attack happened on
OL,18,FSunday 25 June 2023 when Nicolle began
OL,19,Farguing with his partner, accusing her
OL,20,Fof spending too much money and poor
OL,21,Ftimekeeping.
