OL,6,FNicolle lost his temper and spat in
OL,7,Fher face, kicking the table she was
OL,8,Fsitting at and causing her to fall
OL,9,Fbackwards.
OL,11,FHe went on to punch and slap her,
OL,12,Fbruising her eye.
OL,14,FLater that evening, Nicolle grabbed
OL,15,Fhis partner and put both hands around
OL,16,Fher throat, throttling her for up to
OL,17,Fone minute.
